description: THOR was originally designed to develop the THOR Chain backbone and build a balanced, active, and cyclical blockchain ecosystem based on the backbone. Focusing on the blockchain industry, we are committed to providing digital asset holders with a better blockchain ecosystem. Key features include: asset management, financial services, cross-chain payments, POS revenue, P2P lending, DApp ecological portals, and more. In the future, users only need to use the THOR digital application system to experience all the functions of the blockchain ecosystem, and truly realize the one-stop blockchain ecological application platform.
name: THOR Digital Application System
